          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback " href="/book/show/41717392">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21643330-ola-al-najres?shelf=arabic-novels">arabic-novels</a>, 
